Source: pg-tiktoken-c
Section: database
Priority: optional
Maintainer: Ruohang Feng <rh@vonng.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), postgresql-all (>= 217~), libpcre2-dev, pkg-config
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Rules-Requires-Root: no
Homepage: https://github.com/relytcloud/pg_tiktoken_c

Package: postgresql-PGVERSION-pg-tiktoken-c
Architecture: any
Provides: postgresql-pg-tiktoken-c
Depends: ${postgresql:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}
Breaks: ${postgresql:Breaks}
Description: Fast tiktoken BPE tokenizer for PostgreSQL PGVERSION
 pg_tiktoken_c provides OpenAI-compatible token counting, token ID encoding,
 and token-bounded text chunking in PostgreSQL, implemented in C.
